sub_title: International Consultant, Metaverse, Web 3, Futurist, Helping Brands enter The Metaverse,Hospitality, VR XR, Virtual Worlds, Hospitality & Vocational Trainer, Women In AI VR Ambassador APAC.
summary:
VR for softskills and hospitality training , creating modules for training in the field of hospitality and softskills my interest in this has enthused many, and I am also learning every day. I have been creating content now for over 1 year and I have a passion for this which is contagious . Creating Ed Tech through gamification, creating corporate training with learning analytics. 

Worked in Asia for nearly 30 years Hong Kong, China, Thailand and Burma . Presently in Amsterdam , working in VR. Which I became passionate about a few years ago .

Key note speaker and Podcast guest on VR , on boarding , the virtual world . Virtual Presentation and Facilitator .

My Moto is "If you dont ask you dont get"
My Action is if I can dream it I can do it.
 Empowering teams , organisations , people , & providing coaching & training on how to work with new technology remotely and effectively.

With a passion for Vocational Training and CSR 
Building the Future of Communication, Collaboration, & Culture 

International expert for Myanmar : Mentor for Cherie Blair Foundation.
MOPF Ministry of Planning And Finance  International Consultant
Swiss Contact International Consultant
ADB Asian Development Bank International Consultant
Myanmar Pioneering Women Leaders Award Winner & Myanmar's Women's Leader Award Winner
Women In AI Start up Netherlands 
Scottish Woman Of the Year 2003-4 .
